Use Case
	Move ship
Actors
	User, system, ship
Description
	The user holds down a key representing movement. 
	The system reads the key. The system moves the ship
Main Course of Events
Actor			System								Ship
1.Presses key
				2.Read key
 				3.Check if key represents movement
 				4.Check if ship collides with asteroid
 													5.Change ship position according to heading and speed

Alternative Flow of Events
2.1 Wrong key. No change in system
4.1 The ship doesnt exsist
4.2.0 The ship collides with asteroid
4.2.1 The system declares game over